  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3 \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0db3\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two people, including Vasantha, were detained for three months and allowed to be interrogated",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Yesterday (18), the Ministry of Defense allowed the police to detain and interrogate two people, including Wasantha Mudalige, the convenor of that body, who were arrested by the police after a riot held by a group of the Inter-University Student Union.",
        "Detention orders have been issued in accordance with the powers assigned to the Minister of Defense under the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "It is reported that the Ministry of Defense has authorized the police to detain and interrogate Hashan Gunathilake, in addition to the convener of the Inter-University Student Union, Wasantha Mudalige.",
        "The police arrested 16 other people, including Wasantha Mudalige Hashan Gunathilaka, during a demonstration held by the Inter-University Student Union against the government on the 18th.",
        "The 16 suspects who were arrested in this manner were ordered to be released on bail after being presented to the court by the police and the Ministry of Defense has allowed the police to detain and interrogate Wasantha Mudalige Hashan Gunathilaka for a period of 90 days."
      ],
